quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  41,9,"Bola mbu: “toto enywe mukhayanga ulia waloonga eshialo khutsinyanga tsibili, ne mumusasia nende abanyasaye bandi, oyo niye Nyasaye webiloonje biosi.”"
  41,10,"Ne yaramwo tsingulu hekulu washio, ne naramwo ikhabi, nenabalililamwo emikabo chabio khutsinyanga tsine, kano kali habwene muno khubarebanga"
  41,11,"Mana naleng’ana khwikulu nalo nilili omwosi, naliboolela nende eshialo “ itse nimuchamile noho nimukhayile,” biaboola mbu : “ khwitsile nikhuli abarechelefu.”"
  41,12,"Mana naloonga “ amakulu saba” khutsinyanga tsibili, mana nahana buli likulu akalio, mana nikhurona likulu lieshialo khu tsitaa tsiobulindi, esho nishio eshichelo shia Nyasaye Owamani Omumanyi muno"
  41,13,"Ne nibalakabukulamwo oluchendo tawe, boola mbu: “ Ebekanyisilia eshinyasio sholuyoka shinga shiali sha A’ad nende Thamud"
  41,14,"Olwa betselwa nende Abarumwa okhurula imbeli wabu nende inyuma wabu, nibaboolelwa mbu: “ mulalaame shiosi shiosi tawe halali Nyasaye.” nibaboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wefu alenya yakharumile Abamalaika, kho toto efwe khukamwarumwa ninako ako khukhayile.”"
  41,15,"Mana Abandu ba A’ad, Bali abafuru khushialo munjila ilali yatoto tawe, mana nibaboola mbu: “ wina ushila efwe amani ? “ shibalolanga mbu Nyasaye wabaloonga ali namaani okhubashila, Ne bakhayanga ebimanyisio biefu"
  41,16,"Mana nikhubarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka,\tkhutsinyanga tsiamasila, kho banyoole okhupila eshinyasio shiokhubafulafusia, mubulamu bwokhushialo, ni eshinyasio shie indukho ni shokhufulafusia okhukhongo okhushila, Nabo shibalihabinwa tawe"
  41,17,"Ne Abandu ba Thamud khwabalunjisia halali nibachama obuwofu okhushila obulunjifu, mana omulilo kweshinyasio shieshifulafusio, nikubabukula khu kalia kabakholanga"
  41,18,Mana nikhuhabina abasuubila abali nibaria Nyasaye mubo
  41,19,"Ne inyanga yabasuku ba Nyasaye balikhung’asibwa mumulilo, nibakabulwa mumikanda chaukhane"
  41,20,"Olwa balikulakhwo (omulilo oko), amarwi kabu nende tsimoni tsiabu nende amaseelo kabu bilirusia obuloli khu koosi pe kabakholanga"
  41,21,"Ne balireeba amaseelo kemibili chiabu mbu,: “ shina shichila noyinia obuloli khwifwe ?” kaliboola mbu: “ Nyasaye okhulomalomiyie owulomalominjia buli eshindu Naye niye awamulonga olwokhuranga na iwuwe namulikalukha.”"
  41,22,"Shimwali nimunyala okhwifisa tawe, kho amarwi kenyu nende tsimoni tsienyu nende amaseelo kenyu akhubarusilia obuloli, halali mwaparanga mbu toto Nyasaye shiyamanya amaanji kamukholanga tawe"
  41,23,"Ako niko amaparo kenyu, kamuparire Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, kamusishiye, mana nimuba mubalia abatiba"
  41,24,"Ne nibefwila, omulilo nisho eshimenyo shiabu, ne nibasaba eshileshelo shibaleshelwa tawe"